high_descs: Walk one step forward then turn right to face the counter.
Look up and open the cupboard and get the salt shaker.
Turn left and walk to the area to the right of the stove and face it.
Put the salt shaker in the drawer that's under the toaster.
Take a half step right.
Pick up the salt shaker.
Take a half step left.
Put the salt shaker in the drawer with the other one and close it when you're done.
anns.task_desc: Put two salt shakers in the drawer.

high_descs: Walk toward the wall, then hang a right and walk over to the rightmost section of counter and look up at the upper cabinets.
Open the rightmost upper cabinet door and take the salt shaker out of the cabinet then close the door.
Turn left and walk towards the wall, then hang a left and walk up to the section of counter to the right of the oven.
Open the drawer below the counter and put the salt shaker inside in the back left corner.
Turn right and walk towards the window, then turn left to face the counter again.
Pick up the salt shaker off of the counter.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn right and take a step forward, then turn right to face the counter again.
Open the drawer below the counter and put the salt shaker inside to the right of the salt shaker that is already in there.
anns.task_desc: Move two salt shakers into a drawer.

high_descs: Move to the counter to the tight of the sink.
Pick up the shaker from the cabinet
Move to the drawer to the right of the stove
Put the shaker in the drawer
Move over to the right a step
Pick up the shaker from the counter
Move to the drawer to the right of the stove
Put the shaker in the drawer
anns.task_desc: Put two shakers in the drawer to the right of the stove.
